enum enc_flags_e

special encoder flags

Enumerator:
ENC_DISABLE_VUI  don't put vui infromation in sps
ENC_SLICE_TYPE_012  encode slice types as 0,1 or 2 (default is 5,6,7)
ENC_SPS_ONLY_ONCE  put SPS only for the first frame of stream
ENC_REC_POINT_IDR  put recovery point SEI for IDR picture (default is only for non-idr Intra)
ENC_FRAME_PACKING  used together with sei.frame_packing flags. Force encoder to perform actual packing

Definition at line 144 of file v4e_settings.h.

enum interlace_flags_e

interlace flags

Enumerator:
INT_PREDICT_BOTTOM_FROM_TOP  for I and P only coding predict bottom field only from current top field
INT_INTRA_FOR_BOTH_FIELD  encode both fields as intra slices (default is only first intra)
INT_BOTTOM_FIRST  show bottom field first when mbaff, frame or telecine coding (default - top field first)
INT_FORCE_INTERLACE_PICTS  force decoder to play frame-encoded stream as interlaced
INT_MBAFF_BOTTOM_ZERO_POC  put zero POC offsets for both top & bottom fields (for mbaff coding);
INT_MBAFF_USE_FULL_FF_DECIDE  make mbaff frame-field decisions on the macroblock level based on full frame and field pair check
INT_DISABLE_BOTTOM_FIELD_PREPROC  disable preprocessing for bottom field
INT_ADD_TELECINE_PICT_STRUCT  add telecine picture structure for frame-encoded video
INT_TELECINE_START_WITH_3  3-2 start with 3. Together with INT_BOTTOM_FIRST defines start position of telecine

Definition at line 405 of file v4e_settings.h.

enum me_flags_e

Motion Estimation flags.

Can be combined by "|".

Enumerator:
ME_USE_MB_ME_P  Use macroblock level me for P-slices (obsolete).
ME_USE_MB_ME_B  Use macroblock level me for B-slices (obsolete).
ME_USE_SMALL_ME_P  Use preliminary me on the reduced pictures P-slices (obsolete).
ME_USE_SMALL_ME_B  Use preliminary me on the reduced pictures B-slices (obsolete).
ME_LIMIT_B_REFS  Set num_refs for B-frames to (1,1) even if max_refs > 1.
ME_DISABLE_PREPROC_ME  Disable preproc motion estimation by reduced picture.
ME_DISABLE_PREPROC_COMPLEXITY  Disable preproc complexity calculation.
ME_USE_ORIGINAL  use original pixels for motion estimation (obsolete)
ME_USE_FULL_LOG_SEARCH_P  Use more detailed motion estimation for P frames.
ME_USE_FULL_LOG_SEARCH_B  Use more detailed motion estimation for B frames.

enum rate_control_types_e

Types of Rate Control.

Enumerator:
RATE_CONTROL_QP  fixed quality (fixed QP);
RATE_CONTROL_VBR  VBR (HRD: not conforming);.
RATE_CONTROL_CBR  CBR (HRD: VBR mode);.
RATE_CONTROL_CBR_WITH_FILLER  CBR (HRD: CBR mode);.
RATE_CONTROL_DUAL_PASS_0  first pass of dual pass mode;
RATE_CONTROL_DUAL_PASS_1  second pass of dual pass mode;
RATE_CONTROL_INTRA  intra-only mode
RATE_CONTROL_INTRA_WITH_FILLER  intra-only mode with filler

Definition at line 77 of file v4e_settings.h.

enum rc_flags_e

RC (Rate Control) flags.

Enumerator:
RC_IGNORE_VBR_BUFFER_OVERFLOW  ignore buffer overflow for VBR coding
RC_BOUND_MAX_QP_DELTA_B  use qp_delta_b as max for automatically calulated delta_b
RC_BOUND_MIN_QP_DELTA_B  use qp_delta_b as min for automatically calulated delta_b
RC_ADD_FILLER  add filler NALs (can be set in vbr mode if max_kbps is specified)
RC_SET_CBR_FLAG  put cbr_flag into sps (effect only with flag above)
RC_FIXED_GOP_SIZE  support fixed number of bytes in GOP (overflow is not garanteed)
